## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of data up to October 2023. Some sources may not reflect the most current statistics or emerging trends in obesity. Additionally, variations in the definition and measurement of obesity across different studies and regions may affect the comparability of data. Further research is needed to explore the multifaceted causes and potential solutions to the obesity epidemic.